data.description: CONNECTICUT RIVER FRONT home sits high above its 185 ft of water frontage with no flood danger or flood insurance needed. Woodsy location at road’s end adds beauty, privacy, peace. House has 3 beds, 2 full baths, open-concept living & dining room, eat-in kitchen w/ wood stove, 3-season solarium, fireplace, attached garage, carport. Healthy home renovated w/ nontoxic materials, boasts a metal roof, fenced 50 yr old organic gardens with fruit trees & perennials, and 800+ sq ft of multiple level decks from which to watch eagles (and 100 other species of birds) and sunlight dance on the river. MBR opens directly onto stunning private treetop deck. Utility & storage rooms in cellar are sealed from the living space for mold avoidance & added chemical safety. House comfortable and livable now, but buyer will likely want to do some of own upgrades. Convenient, yet hidden location just 20 min to Northampton, Amherst, Springfield. Price reduced for quick sale.
